                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320405-220-off1301 t18320405-220-cd1302"></join>, 1 cruet top, value 5s., and 1 spoon, value 5s., the goods of the <rs id="t18320405-220-viclabel1303" type="occupation">Rev</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320405-220-victim1907 t18320405-220-viclabel1303"></join>. 
                     
