               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18320405-220-person1908">
                  RICHARD 
                  BRITTING
               <interp inst="t18320405-220-person1908" type="surname" value="BRITTING"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18320405-220-person1908" type="given" value="RICHARD"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18320405-220-person1908" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live at the Rev. Hugh Hodgson, in <placeName id="t18320405-220-crimeloc1304">Dean-street, Westminster</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18320405-220-crimeloc1304" type="placeName" value="Dean-street, Westminster"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18320405-220-crimeloc1304" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320405-220-off1301 t18320405-220-crimeloc1304"></join>. On the 6th of March, between two and three o'clock, I was in the kitchen - something drew my attention to the window, and on going towards the passage, I saw the door open, which I had shut not ten minutes before; I went by the pantry, and missed the top of a mustard-pot and a spoon - I ran up the area, and saw the prisoner walking on the terrace, within twenty yards of the area - I walked past them; I collared Bailey - Reece immediately ran away; I called Stop thief! and he was stopped by Lloyd - he threw the spoon over into the garden, and the mustard top was found in his pocket - nothing was found on Bailey; they were within a yard of each other, and appeared in company.</p>
               <p>Cross-examined by MR. HEATON. Q. Had you seen a person loitering about for two or three days before? A. No, I never said so.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18320405-220-person1909">
                  EDWARD 
                  LLOYD
               <interp inst="t18320405-220-person1909" type="surname" value="LLOYD"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18320405-220-person1909" type="given" value="EDWARD"></interp>
